frac{\\cot\\phi}{r^2} u_{\\phi} +\\frac{1}{r^2\\sin^2\\phi}u_{\\theta\\theta} = 0 \n","\\end{align*}$\n","\n","$\\theta$ 에 무관하므로 \n",">$\\begin{align*}\n"," u_{rr} +\\frac{2}{r} u_r &+\\frac{1}{r^2}u_{\\phi\\phi} +\\frac{\\cot\\phi}{r^2} u_{\\phi}  = 0 \n","\\end{align*}$\n","\n","그 다음 변수분리 한다.\n",">$\\displaystyle u(r,\\phi)=R(r)\\Phi(\\phi)$\n","\n","따라서 두 개의 상미분방정식(ODEs)으로 나타낼 수 있다.\n",">$\\begin{align*}\n"," sin\\phi\\, \\Phi''+ cos\\phi\\, \\Phi'+\\lambda \\sin\\phi \\Phi= 0 \\;\\;\\;\\text{Legendre's equation}\\\\\n","\\end{align*}$\n","\n",">$\\begin{align*}\n","r^2R'' +2rR' -\\lambda R = 0 \\;\\;\\; \\text{Euler's equation}\n","\\end{align*}$\n","\n","1)$\\begin{align*}\n"," sin\\phi\\, \\Phi''+ cos\\phi\\, \\Phi'+\\lambda \\sin\\phi \\Phi= 0 \n","\\end{align*}$\n","\n",">$x=\\cos\\phi$ 로 치환한다.  $\\displaystyle(0 \\leq \\phi \\leq \\pi$)\n","\n","$\\begin{align*}\n","(1 -x^2) \\frac{d^2\\Phi}{dx^2} &-2x\\frac{d\\Phi}{dx} +\\lambda \\Phi = 0 \\; \\;(-1 \\leq x \\leq 1 )\\\\\n"," &\\Downarrow \\\\\n","\\frac{d}{dx} \\left[ (1 -x^2) \\frac{d\\Phi}{dx} \\right] &+\\lambda \\Phi = 0 \n","\\end{align*}$\n","\n",">고유값은 \n","$\\lambda=n(n +1)$, $n=0,1,2,\\cdots$ \n","\n",">고유함수는 \n","$\\Phi(\\phi)$ = $P_n(x)$ = $P_n(cos\\phi)$\n","\n","$P_n(x)$는 Legendre polynomials이다.\n","\n","$\\begin{align*}\n"," &P_n(x) = \\frac{1}{2^n n!} \\frac{d^n}{dx^n} \\left[ (x^2 -1)^n \\right]\n","\\end{align*}$\n","\n","2) $\\begin{align*}\n","r^2R'' +2rR' -\\lambda R = 0 \n","\\end{align*}$\n",">$R_n(r)= a_n r^n + b_n r^{-(n +1)} \\;\\;\\xrightarrow\\;\\;a_n r^n$\n","\n","따라서 $\\displaystyle u(r,\\phi)=R(r)\\Phi(\\phi)$ 이므로\n",">$\\displaystyle u(r,\\phi) = \\sum_{n=0}^\\infty a_n r^n P_n(\\cos\\phi)\\;\\;\\;$ \n","\n","경계조건(BC)는 $\\displaystyle u(R,\\phi) = g(\\phi)$\n",">$\\displaystyle g(\\phi) = \\sum_{n=0}^\\infty a_n R^n P_n(\\cos\\phi)$\n","\n","위의 식 양변에 $P_m(\\cos\\phi)\\sin\\phi$을 곱하고, $\\phi$에 대해 $0$에서부터 $\\pi$까지 적분한다.\n","\n",">$\\begin{align*}\n"," \\int_0^\\pi g(\\phi) P_m(\\cos\\phi)\\,\\sin\\phi \\,d\\phi &= \n","   \\sum_{n=0}^\\infty a_n  R^n\\int_0^{\\pi} P_n(\\cos\\phi) P_m(\\cos\\phi)\\,\\sin\\phi \\, d\\phi \\\\\n"," &= \\sum_{n=0}^\\infty a_n  R^n\\int_{-1}^1 P_n(x) P_m(x) \\,dx \\\\ \n"," &=\n"," \\begin{cases}\n","  \\;\\;\\;\\;\\, 0  & n \\neq m \\\\ \n","  \\displaystyle \\frac{2}{2m +1}\\, a_m & n = m \n"," \\end{cases} \\\\ \n"," &\\Downarrow \\\\ \n"," a_n &=\\frac{2n +1}{2 R^n} \\int_0^{\\pi} g(\\phi) P_n(\\cos\\phi)\\, \\sin \\phi \\,d\\phi\n","\\end{align*}$\n","\n","따라서 $u(r,\\phi)$은 다음과 같다.\n",">$\\begin{align*}\n","u(r,\\phi) = \\sum_{n=0}^\\infty (\\frac{2n +1}{2} \\int_0^{\\pi} g(\\phi) P_n(\\cos\\phi)\\, \\sin \\phi \\,d\\phi)(\\frac{r^n}{R^n})P_n(\\cos\\phi)\n","\\end{align*}$ "]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"2Dn_mYGjy9Tb","colab_type":"text"},"source":["(b) $\\displaystyle u(r,\\phi,\\theta) = \\int_0^{2\\pi} \\int_0^\\pi K(r,\\phi,\\theta; R,\\varphi,\\vartheta)\\, g(\\varphi,\\vartheta) \\sin\\varphi \\,d\\varphi \\, d\\vartheta$"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"v35iaMP6f-Zk","colab_type":"text"},"source":["\n","## <문제 2> Poisson's Equation for the Sphere"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"XUYLzXN8f-Zn","colab_type":"text"},"source":["We consider the problem\n","\n",">$\\begin{align*}\n"," u_{rr} +\\frac{2}{r} u_r &+\\frac{1}{r^2}u_{\\phi\\phi} +\\frac{\\cot\\phi}{r^2} u_{\\phi} +\\frac{1}{r^2\\sin^2\\phi}u_{\\theta\\theta} = -F(r,\\phi,\\theta), \\;\\; r < R \\\\ \n"," u(R,\\phi,\\theta) &= 0\\\\ \n","\\end{align*}$\n","\n","(a) Solve by taking the finite Fourier Transforms.\n","\n","(b) Derive $G(r,\\phi,\\theta; \\rho,\\varphi,\\vartheta)$ in the equivalent integral formula:\n","\n",">$\\displaystyle u(r,\\phi,\\theta) = \\int_0^{2\\pi} \\int_0^\\pi \\int_0^R G(r,\\phi,\\theta; \\rho,\\varphi,\\vartheta)\\, F(\\rho, \\varphi,\\vartheta) \\,\\rho^2 \\sin\\varphi \\,d\\rho \\,d\\varphi \\, d\\vartheta$"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"1yn2tlTt02gl","colab_type":"text"},"source":["###<풀이>"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"XPmKHGnn1GqX","colab_type":"text"},"source":["(a) finite Fourer Transforms은 다음과 같다.\n",">$\\begin{align*}\n"," \\mathcal{F}_s[f]&=\\frac{2}{L} \\int_0^L f(x)\\,\\sin\\frac{n\\pi x}{L} \\,dx =b_n &\\;\\;\\;\\text{Finite Sine Transform} \\\\ \n"," \\mathcal{F}_c[f]&=\\frac{2}{L} \\int_0^L f(x)\\,\\cos\\frac{n\\pi x}{L} \\,dx =a_n &\\;\\;\\;\\text{Finite Cosine Transform}\n","\\end{align*}\n","$\n","\n","역변환은 다음과 같다.\n",">$\\begin{align*}\n"," f(x) &=\\sum_{n=1}^{\\infty} b_n \\sin\\frac{n\\pi x}{L} &\\;\\;\\;\\text{Inverse Sine Transform} \\\\ \n"," f(x) &= \\frac{a_0}{2} +\\sum_{n=1}^\\infty a_n \\cos \\frac{n\\pi x}{L} &\\;\\;\\;\\text{Inverse Cosine Transform}\n","\\end{align*}$\n","\n","\n"," $u(R,\\phi,\\theta) = 0$이므로 Sine Transform을 사용한다.\n","\n","\n","$\\theta$ 에 무관하므로 \n",">$\\begin{align*}\n"," u_{rr} + \\frac{2}{r} u_r &+\\frac{1}{r^2}u_{\\phi\\phi} +\\frac{\\cot\\phi}{r^2} u_{\\phi}  = -F(r,\\phi) \n","\\end{align*}$\n","\n",">$\\begin{align*}\n"," \\mathcal{F}_s [u_\\phi] &= \\frac{d \\mathcal{F}_s [u]}{d\\phi} \\\\ \n"," \\mathcal{F}_s [u_{\\phi\\phi}] &= \\frac{d^2 \\mathcal{F}_s [u]}{d\\phi^2} \\\\ \n"," \\mathcal{F}_s [u_r] &= -\\frac{n\\pi}{L} \\mathcal{F}_c [u] \\\\\n"," \\mathcal{F}_s [u_{rr}]&= -\\left( \\frac{n\\pi}{L} \\right)^2 \\mathcal{F}_s [u] +\\frac{2n\\pi}{L^2}  \\left[ u(0,\\phi) -(-1)^n u(L,\\phi) \\right]\\\\ \n"," \\end{align*}$\n","\n"," r<R이므로 L은 R이다.\n","\n","$\\begin{align*}\n","\\mathcal{F}_s [u]=\\mathcal{F}_c [u]=U_n(\\phi)\n"," \\end{align*}$\n","\n","변환하면 다음과 같다.\n",">$\\begin{align*}\n","-\\left( \\frac{n\\pi}{R} \\right)^2 U_n(\\phi) + \\frac{2n\\pi}{R^2} \\left[ u(0,\\phi) -(-1)^n u(R,\\phi) \\right] + \\frac{2}{r}(-\\frac{n\\pi}{R}U_n(\\phi))  +\\frac{1}{r^2}( \\frac{d^2 U_n(\\phi)}{d\\phi^2})+\\frac{\\cot\\phi}{r^2}(\\frac{d U_n(\\phi)}{d\\phi})=-S_n(\\phi)\n"," \\end{align*}$  \n","\n",">$\\begin{align*}\n"," F(\\phi) &=\\sum_{n=1}^{\\infty} S_n(\\phi) \\sin\\frac{n\\pi \\phi}{R} \n","\\end{align*}$\n","\n",">$\\begin{align*}\n","S_n(\\phi) = \\frac{2}{R} \\int_0^R  F(\\phi)\\sin\\frac{n\\pi \\phi}{R}d\\phi\n","\\end{align*}$\n","\n","$ u(R,\\phi,\\theta)= 0 $"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"CHOZcEg637kJ","colab_type":"text"},"source":["(b) $\\displaystyle u(r,\\phi,\\theta) = \\int_0^{2\\pi} \\int_0^\\pi \\int_0^R G(r,\\phi,\\theta; \\rho,\\varphi,\\vartheta)\\, F(\\rho, \\varphi,\\vartheta) \\,\\rho^2 \\sin\\varphi \\,d\\rho \\,d\\varphi \\, d\\vartheta$ "]}]}